item.title: Anyone have cirno pk or stork pk source?
item.dc:creator: @Zach_Knight Zach Knight
item.description:
@Zach_Knight wrote:

I have it.

I don’t even think I modified anything in landscape. As I recall, there had been modifications to the landscape at one time, but I’d gone to the trouble of reverting them at some revision to match classic better; all I changed was re-adding the wilderness gate I believe, though.

What is it specifically that you wanted? I used all original landscape features for all of the features.
